title: Charming Furnished Studio, Doormen, East 86th & York, No Broker Fee
posting_body: ['Charming Furnished Studio for annual rental, no broker fee.', ' Renovated in 2021.', ' Full-service doorman building with laundry downstairs.', ' Dressing area outside bathroom provides lots of closet space and storage.', '  Queen bed from West Elm.', 'Very quiet, with lovely views from large picture window facing south.', 'Great neighborhood with lots of restaurants, cafes etc.', 'Easy walk over to beautiful Carl Schurz Park and the NY Ferry docks at 89th street.', 'Or, if you need a subway, walk over to 86th Street at 2nd avenue for the Q train to the theater district, and/or the catch the Lexington Avenue subway (4,5,6) at 86th Street and Lexington Avenue.', 'Crosstown bus is right outside across 86th Street.', 'No broker fee however there are a few fees required from the Management company - a $350 non-refundable application fee, a $110 non-refundable credit check fee, a $500 non-refundable move in/out fee, and a $1000 REFUNDABLE fee that the management company holds during tenancy.', ' Application requires proof of income & funds, and Board approval,  so serious inquires only please.', ' Sorry no pets for tenant (Building restriction).', 'NO GUARANTORS PERMITTED.', ' Owner looking for lease to begin anytime in August, September or October, pending Board approval.', 'Call Sue at 917-392-0066.']
